#

Pumpkin and Sage Stuffing

45 min
$8.5
250 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 6

Allergens:

Gluten

Dietary Tags:

Vegetarian

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Side Dish

Tags:

Comfort FoodSide DishFall Flavor

Description

A savory and aromatic stuffing that combines the earthy sweetness of pumpkin with the fragrant notes of sage, perfect for a comforting side dish.

Ingredients

  • bread cubes: 4 cups
  • pumpkin puree: 1 cup
  • chicken or vegetable broth: 1 cup
  • sage (fresh or dried): 2 tablespoons
  • onion (chopped): 1 medium
  • celery (chopped): 1 cup
  • garlic (minced): 2 cloves
  • olive oil: 2 tablespoons
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
